11,"uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T03:20:47.000Z","msg":"擺明同支那軍方合作竊取各國政府機密資料"},{"pid":"12d21a43ddff6aabcf59a88051aae7de9f0ffb86","tid":934611,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T03:57:29.000Z","msg":"女人最守唔到秘密，叫幾條黑腸嚇下佢咩都講晒出黎"}]}